sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7a8e51dc33111c83d01f58af29d0d63e3e7b1e0","tid":2277784,"uid":266051,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T15:33:10.000Z","msg":"本身有嘅病係唔會保你，危疾主要保你買果陣冇果啲<br />\n<br />\n既然保唔到，做乜哂錢買"},{"pid":"e519c81ac305488f7813ff484b318b84d6282216","tid":2277784,"uid":131757,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d7a8e51dc33111c83d01f58af29d0d63e3e7b1e0","tid":2277784,"uid":266051,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T15:33:10.000Z","msg":"本身有嘅病係唔會保你，危疾主要保你買果陣冇果啲<br />\n<br />\n既然保唔到，做乜哂錢買"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T17:11:39.000Z","msg":"而家冇病,驚有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"958a1445f56cbc3606e8562d3ac21ba5c6f4055a","tid":2277784,"uid":314845,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T02:32:01.000Z","msg":"無儲蓄成份既危疾通常都無得供斷，係消費型既 當然保費係初期會便好多 但如果到50幾60歲之後要交既保費就會貴好多 你要自己計下數<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/Ngating\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FNgating&d=TOASGvm2FfjCvYiV2fDq78yZng7V5AOcQmv89xdKlzQ%3D&h=bc80153c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/Ngating</a>"},{"pid":"85c94e9aa988efccf21b89c95cd41473aa0afc69","tid":2277784,"uid":163660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"77328b54c71dd4b85d736d44467e9df5af121b7c","tid":2277784,"uid":383581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T14:42:25.000Z","msg":"搭單問，到底應該買危疾定醫保呢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T02:42:58.000Z","msg":"危疾係for患大病返唔到工嘅期間的生活費<br />\n如果budget有限，建議一定做醫療先，有多餘錢先再諗危疾，醫療嘅槓桿大好多，一般廿幾三十歲嘅人，幾舊水一個月換成千萬保額，至少唔需要再擔心住院開支～<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n秒回 任問<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/sysylll\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fsysylll&d=TOASGvm2FfjCvYiV2fDq78yZng7V5AOcQmv89xdKlzQ%3D&h=e50c1e1c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/sysylll</a>"},{"pid":"e1b328b82b9e7d25