返<br />\n5.實報實銷，先自己比錢，再攞張單去claim<br />\n<br />\n儲蓄型：<br />\n1.後生入場費貴少少，唔會加價<br />\n2.賠償額會隨通賬增加<br />\n3.最快10年供斷，終身總保費較平<br />\n4.約25年後回本，有需要可cut單取回所有保費（多個選擇但唔建議咁做）<br />\n5.幾日內收全額賠償支票，唔駛動用積蓄<br />\n<br />\n總結：<br />\n兩邊買，50歲後cut消費型，儲蓄型保單個賠償額會加到去足夠晚年保障<br />\n<br />\n希望解答到你"},{"pid":"63d9ab2426beb33df21772aca1b1244654d706be","tid":2277784,"uid":206889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T03:39:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/Jetkoong\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FJetkoong&d=TOASGvm2FfjCvYiV2fDq78yZng7V5AOcQmv89xdKlzQ%3D&h=35240832\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/Jetkoong</a> 小弟manulife 傾傾"},{"pid":"4ba7313a8a0f17c9a124e64cfff15aca299f8daf","tid":2277784,"uid":385789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T15:50:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}